<body>
    <h1>Profile Update (Associate) (Use Case =E2=80=93 UC12)</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h3 id=3D"ProfileUpdate(Associate)(UseCase=E2=80=93UC12)-ProfileUpd=
ateworkflow">Profile Update workflow</h3>
<p>Table-27</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"6=
7eb0285-d8ca-4b84-a7b1-25f8a7deca61" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 217.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 1582.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Type</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Profile Update</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Description</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>This Profile Update use case manages the user personal data changes in O=
racle HR.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of Attributes&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The following set of attributes represent the tentative set of users=E2=
=80=99 attributes which will be used in the process flow. The final set of =
source and target attributes will be finalized in the solution design docum=
ent.</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>First Name</p></li>
<li>
<p>Last Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Person Number</p></li>
<li>
<p>Location</p></li>
</ol>
<p></p>
<p>Refer Appendix =E2=80=9C<a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://drive=
.google.com/drive/folders/17u4oN4VdyLijziIcn8PMSlUxT5HS_LW0" rel=3D"nofollo=
w"><u>Source and Target Attribute Mapping</u></a>=E2=80=9D for complete lis=
t of attribute mapping.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Pre-Conditions</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>User is already present in SailPoint IdentityIQ with existing accounts a=
nd access details.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Change in user profile attributes values like first name, last name etc.=
</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Oracle HR will send the updated user attributes to SailPoint IdentityIQ.=
</p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ provisions the updated user profile attributes valu=
es like first name, last name etc.</p></li>
<li>
<p>The updates will be propagated to downstream applications.&nbsp;</p></li=
>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of downstream applications</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Active Directory, Azure, GSuite, ServiceNow, Oracle ERP Cloud, Oracle EP=
M Cloud, OCI.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Acceptance criteria</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ will receive user personal data updates which will =
be propagated to downstream applications.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Error handling</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Email notification will be sent to the Ascension Health Alliance support=
 team managing the SailPoint IdentityIQ platform.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Persona / Actors</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Automated Process</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p></p>
<p><strong>Dependency:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1003" data-layout=3D"center" data-local-id=3D"ef=
877718-c5a8-4827-8fda-8455864b5003" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 114.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 213.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 676.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>S. no</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Dependency</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Point of contact for answers</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>1</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of attributes</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to send the final set of attributes ma=
pping</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to finalize the attributes and its val=
ues required for trigger</p>
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to provide users=E2=80=99 attributes f=
or which value change is detected and downstream application whose accounts=
 attributes are updated</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to finalize the attributes and its val=
ues required in the Basic Flow</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p></p>
